headline: Hispanic Chamber of Metro Orlando and Prospera Honor Remarkable Leaders at the 28th Don Quijote Awards Gala
summary: Prospera and the Hispanic Chamber of Metro Orlando co-hosted the 28th annual Don Quijote Awards Gala on December 13, 2025, at Epcot's World Showplace Pavilion. The prestigious annual celebration brought together business and community leaders across Central Florida to honor outstanding Hispanic entrepreneurs and professionals whose leadership and perseverance continue to drive economic and community impact.
